r7263 | pdox@google.com | Tue Nov 22 14:00:03 PST 2011

Changed paths:
 M http://src.chromium.org/viewvc/native_client/trunk/src/native_client/pnacl/driver/pnacl-nativeld.py?r1=7263&amp;r2=7262&amp;pathrev=7263
 M http://src.chromium.org/viewvc/native_client/trunk/src/native_client/pnacl/driver/pnacl-translate.py?r1=7263&amp;r2=7262&amp;pathrev=7263

Make sure paths to the sandboxed tools are evaluated lazily.

This change is needed because the expression evaluator evaluates both sides of a ternary.
Using variable name expansion only evaluates the expression needed.

This ensures that BASE_NACL will only be resolved when --pnacl-sb is given.

